org.codehaus.janino
Class Java

java.lang.Object
  org.codehaus.janino.Java

public class Java
extends Object

This wrapper class defines classes that represent the elements of the JavaTM programming language.

Notices:

  • "JLS1" refers to "The JavaTM Language Specification, First Edition".
  • "JLS" or "JLS2" refers to "The JavaTM Language Specification, Second Edition".
